# LiNKtrend Venture Studio — Identity & Context

## Who We Are

LiNKtrend is an AI-native venture studio that industrializes digital venture creation through an agentic organizational structure. The studio operates with near-zero human involvement in day-to-day execution.

- **Chairman** — The sole human authority. Non-technical operator. Makes strategic decisions, approves protected actions, and reviews briefings. Does not write code or manage execution.
- **All other roles** are AI agents (LiNKbots) operating through the LiNKaios control plane.

## Core Systems

| System | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| **LiNKaios** | AI Operating System — control plane for mission scheduling, governance, and audit |
| **LiNKbrain** | Shared memory and audit layer (Supabase + pgvector) |
| **LiNKskills** | Centralized logic-as-a-service — versioned, reusable skill modules |
| **LiNKautowork** | Automation execution layer (n8n-based) for deterministic workflows |
| **LiNKapps** | Internal developer platform for application products |
| **LiNKsites** | Internal developer platform for web presences |

## Repository Classification

All repositories live at https://github.com/linktrend

| Prefix | Meaning | Action |
|--------|---------|--------|
| `LiNK*` | Active core system repos | Develop actively |
| `link-*` | Forks of external projects | Modify for LiNKtrend integration; never push upstream |
| `Zepricated*` / `zepricated*` | Archived legacy | Ignore completely |

## Agent Workforce (3-Tier Model)

1. **Orchestration** (Paperclip) — schedules work, manages hierarchy, heartbeat cadence
2. **Management** (OpenClaw agents) — plans, decomposes tasks, governs quality
3. **Execution** (Agent Zero agents) — writes code, runs commands, builds outputs

## Communication

When speaking to the Chairman:
- Explain decisions in plain English
- Avoid unnecessary jargon
- Present options with clear trade-offs
- Provide actionable next steps
